{
  "chapter": 37,
  "chapter_summary": "将军府混战继续，厉南星以玄铁宝剑助公孙燕击退高大成、杜大业，又怒踢帅孟雄报一掌之仇。厉南星被史白都一掌击落假山，生死未卜，临危将玄铁宝剑掷给金逐流。金逐流持剑与史白都、文道庄苦战，为史红英驱除修罗阴煞功寒气。公孙燕误信厉南星已死，悲愤之下拼死攻向史白都。文道庄挂念受伤之子文胜中，精神不能集中。上官泰赶到击退帅孟雄，李敦夫妇杀死董十三娘。宇文雄等江海天门人弟子及时赶到，战局逆转。文道庄救下被封妙嫦追杀的文胜中，命其子杀死秦元浩。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "厉南星",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "text": "燕妹，你快去接应李敦夫妻！",
      "tone": "焦急"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "帅孟雄",
      "listener": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "text": "好呀，你这小子也来送死！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "厉南星",
      "listener": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "text": "那姓贺的老妖妇早已死了，你到黄泉路上会她去吧！",
      "tone": "冷笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_nan_xing",
      "speaker_name": "厉南星",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "贤弟，接剑！",
      "tone": "大叫"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "speaker_name": "文道庄",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "我倒要试试你这玄铁宝剑的威力！",
      "tone": "认真"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "text": "好，那就来吧！",
      "tone": "豪迈"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "挡我者死，让我者生！",
      "tone": "豪迈"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "没，没什么。",
      "tone": "犹豫"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "你怎么啦？",
      "tone": "担心"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "别为我耽误了，快去救厉大哥要紧！",
      "tone": "焦急"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "是！",
      "tone": "认真"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "厉南星早已给我杀掉啦，你到黄泉路上会他去吧！",
      "tone": "得意"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "你敢诅咒我的厉大哥，吃我一剑！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "金逐流，你偷了我的玄铁宝剑，你以为我就奈何不了你吗？休说一剑，十剑百剑，只有何妨？",
      "tone": "冷笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "臭丫头，躲开！我不想亲手杀你！",
      "tone": "冷酷"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_qian_feng",
      "speaker_name": "沙千峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "乖侄女，有本领你就再打我一鞭吧。",
      "tone": "嘲讽"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_qian_feng",
      "speaker_name": "沙千峰",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "好呀，你这个臭丫头还要逞强。",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_sha_qian_feng",
      "text": "沙伯伯，这一鞭是你叫我打的！",
      "tone": "冷笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "speaker_name": "史红英",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "别再顾我了，你自己逃吧。",
      "tone": "悲伤"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "speaker_name": "金逐流",
      "listener": "char_shi_hong_ying",
      "text": "生则同生，死则同死！",
      "tone": "豪迈"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "speaker_name": "文道庄",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "可惜，可惜，我来迟了一步！但也不算太迟。",
      "tone": "调侃"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "speaker_name": "文道庄",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "好吧，既然是你的吩咐，那我就只好得罪令妹了！",
      "tone": "调侃"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "text": "你替我拿这个臭丫头，金逐流这小子不是我的对手。",
      "tone": "认真"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "厉大哥，厉大哥！咦！厉大哥，你怎么啦？你在哪儿？",
      "tone": "焦急"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "史白都这厮欺侮孩儿，爹爹，你还不快来帮我？",
      "tone": "焦急"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "text": "我和你爹爹是好朋友，你别胡闹，赶快走吧！",
      "tone": "认真"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_sheng_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "文胜中",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "text": "姓厉这小子早已给史帮主杀啦，你这小妞儿还是跟了我吧！",
      "tone": "嘲讽"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "text": "我看在你爹爹份上，指点你一条生路，你自己要来找死，我可不和你客气了！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "厉南星是不是你杀，是不是你杀的？",
      "tone": "痛苦"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "text": "原来你是喜欢上这小子呀，这小子有什么好？不错，是我杀的！乖侄女，你莫伤心，我赔你一个女婿就是。",
      "tone": "嘲讽"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_sun_yan",
      "speaker_name": "公孙燕",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "厉大哥死了，我也不想活啦！你杀了我，自有爹爹给我报仇。史白都，今日我和你拼了。",
      "tone": "悲痛"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "speaker_name": "文道庄",
      "listener": "char_wen_sheng_zhong",
      "text": "胜中，你怎么啦？",
      "tone": "担心"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_sheng_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "文胜中",
      "listener": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "text": "我给那臭丫头伤了，爹，你要为我报仇！",
      "tone": "痛苦"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "speaker_name": "文道庄",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "他好像伤得很重。",
      "tone": "担心"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "text": "令郎决死不了，我听得出来，你放心吧。",
      "tone": "平静"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "text": "死不了的。就是死了，这也是为皇上尽力。",
      "tone": "冷酷"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "speaker_name": "安俊庭",
      "listener": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "text": "贺大娘已给那姓厉的小子杀了。",
      "tone": "恐惧"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "帅孟雄",
      "listener": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "text": "什么，她已经死了？",
      "tone": "惊讶"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_can_jiang",
      "speaker_name": "参将",
      "listener": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "text": "东西两面城门已给‘贼兵’攻破，张、孟两位统领请将军出去亲自督师，否则恐怕是守不住了。",
      "tone": "焦急"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "帅孟雄",
      "listener": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "text": "好，我马上出去督军。安副将，你把府中的弓箭手尽都调来，叫他们换上毒箭，将这几个小贼乱箭射杀！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "speaker_name": "安俊庭",
      "listener": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "text": "不怕误伤了史白都和文道庄吗？",
      "tone": "疑问"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "帅孟雄",
      "listener": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "text": "哪还顾得了这么多！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": "char_shuai_meng_xiong",
      "text": "帅孟雄，吃我一掌。",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_shi_sang_niang",
      "speaker_name": "董十三娘",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "哪里来的这个老匹夫？",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_cai_feng",
      "speaker_name": "何彩凤",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "text": "这妖妇最为可恶，上官前辈，不能饶她！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": "char_an_jun_ting",
      "text": "岂有此理，连我你们也要射杀了！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yu_wen_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "宇文雄",
      "listener": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "text": "好，你是六合帮的帮主是吗？我倒要看看你有什么厉害？",
      "tone": "豪迈"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_guang_xia",
      "speaker_name": "李光夏",
      "listener": "char_jin_zhu_liu",
      "text": "小师叔，小师叔！",
      "tone": "欣喜"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_bai_du",
      "speaker_name": "史白都",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要命的就来送死！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_tai",
      "speaker_name": "上官泰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "义军已经破城，要性命的快快投降。",
      "tone": "严肃"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_feng_miao_chang",
      "speaker_name": "封妙嫦",
      "listener": "char_wen_sheng_zhong",
      "text": "我与你有什么情？哼，我若放你过去，倒显得是我行为不端了！",
      "tone": "冷笑"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_sheng_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "文胜中",
      "listener": "char_feng_miao_chang",
      "text": "嫦妹，请念在昔日之情，放我过去吧！",
      "tone": "恳求"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "speaker_name": "文道庄",
      "listener": "char_feng_miao_chang",
      "text": "休得伤害我儿！",
      "tone": "愤怒"
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wen_sheng_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "文胜中",
      "listener": "char_wen_dao_zhuang",
      "text": "爹，你替我把这小子杀了！",
      "tone": "痛苦"
    }
  ],
